Class Course

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DataObject>

    public class Course
extends DataObject
    Class representing a course. A Course must have an owner (User) id, a (possibly empty) set of Users and a(possibly empty) set of Domains. Only the teacher may add/remove domains and learners.
